# ===========================
# QUESTIONS & REPONSES
# ===========================

### Ajouter une question avec ses réponses
POST {{host}}/questions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "evaluationId": "3669f89a-bb4d-498e-b003-0dd293101306",
  "questionText": "Quelle est la solution de 2x = 44 ?",
  "answers": [
    { "answerText": "x = 42", "isCorrect": false },
    { "answerText": "x = 22", "isCorrect": true }
  ]
}

###

### Modifier une question
PATCH {{host}}/questions/449ad326-7d2c-44cc-aa6a-3b7f440458b0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "questionText": "Quelle est la valeur de x si 2x = 4 ?"
}

###

### Supprimer une question
DELETE {{host}}/questions/e758d0f0-1d2a-4a6e-8f99-bb1c751b8e91
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

